Thank you all for participating. The Giveaway is now closed. Results will be out within a week or so and will be posted here. Thanks and have a great week ahead!

[GIVEAWAY -  GOPRO HERO 8]
.
#iwantagoprohero8 
This year, I am hosting this SPECIAL BIRTHDAY GIVEAWAY to raise awareness of Dads for Life (@CentreForFathering) who has inspired me to be a more involved Dad. Here's how you can win a brand new GoPro Hero8 Action Camera (worth SGD500)!
.
From family travels, celebrations to events and milestones, I use my trusty GoPro Cameras all the time to capture family memories. I would not be able to capture these precious snorkeling shots from our @holidayinnresortmaldives vacation last year without my GoPro.
.
For a chance to win your very own GoPro Hero 8, simply:
.
1) LIKE this post and FOLLOW @Doting_Dad and @CentreForFathering IG accounts.
.
2) SUBSCRIBE to our Youtube channel at https://m.youtube.com/lifestinymiracles (Click bio for direct link).
.
3)  COMMENT which are your favorite GoPro Hero 8 features and share a memorable activity which you, as a Dad (or your husband), did with the family during this #CircuitBreaker season.
.
4) TAG at least 5 other Dads/Moms in the comments below.  Type only one name per comment.
.
5) BONUS ENTRY: SHARE this exclusive giveaway on your FB/IG and tag me@doting_dad.
.
T&C:
1) This giveaway is not affiliated with Instagram or Facebook. 
2) The giveaway ends 28 June 2020 (2359hours). The judges' decision is final. 
3) Entries which do not fulfill all mandatory criteria will be disqualified. 
4) The winner will be notified by private message and must acknowledge within 24 hours, otherwise prize will be redrawn.
5) This giveaway is open to all Dads residing in Singapore only (Mummies can join but their Hubbies must follow @doting_dad and @CentreForFathering IG. We will ask for their usernames as verification).
6) The winner has to self-collect the prize at an agreed time and location convenient to the sponsor. All the best!
.

My favourite features of GoPro Hero 8 are their best in class digital stabilisation and improved microphone that allows me to capture the best quality videos! During this circuit breaker, I really appreciate my hubby because he cooks almost every meal and he always cook our favourite dishes. He also upcycled many things and made it into fun craft and toys for my daughter to play, this is indeed memorable for her! Whenever I'm feeling down, he will cheer me up by saying" Marriage is like a workshop-where the hubby works and the wife shops 😂"We both love him to the moon and back! Reposted and followed both! Thanks for the awesome giveaway! Followed on YouTube :Chen Peiyu @missy_luvs_my

Hope to bring along a GoPro Hero8 on our next gaigai! Completed all steps. @yujun8

I definitely love the new features such as capture presets, live burst photos and HyperSmooth 2.0 which makes this action camera so powerful and a must have! As a dad, the most memorable activity I did with my daughter during this Circuit breaker period was to make bubble tea together from scratch. She had cravings for Bubble tea as all shops were closed previously. We did a pretty good job, perhaps we could open a bubble tea shop the next time 😜 Followed both and reposted on story! Thanks @doting_dad and @centreforfathering for this awesome giveaway! Followed Youtube :Kelvin Chow @rainbowshines831
